<h2 id="sec:use-of-x.509-certificates-at-the-mtp-layer">4.1 Use of X.509 certificates at the MTP layer<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:use-of-x.509-certificates-at-the-mtp-layer" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h2>

<h3 id="sec:purpose-126">Purpose<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:purpose-126" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<p>The purpose of this test is to ensure the EUT can use X.509 certificates
to secure communication at the MTP layer.</p>

<h3 id="sec:functionality-tags-37">Functionality Tags<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:functionality-tags-37" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<p>Mandatory</p>

<h3 id="sec:test-setup-128">Test Setup<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:test-setup-128" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<ol>
<li>Ensure that the EUT and test equipment have the necessary information to send
and receive USP Records to each other.</li>
<li>Ensure that the use of MTP layer encryption is enabled on the EUT.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="sec:test-procedure-119">Test Procedure<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:test-procedure-119" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<ol>
<li>Send a GetSupportedProtocol message to the EUT with the following structure:</li>
</ol>

<pre><code filter="pbv" type="Msg">header {
    msg_id: '&lt;msg_id&gt;'
    msg_type: GET_SUPPORTED_PROTO
}
body {
    request {
        get_supported_protocol {
            controller_supported_protocol_versions: '&lt;comma separated list of test controller versions&gt;'
        }
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="sec:test-metrics-127">Test Metrics<a class="headerlink" href="04-index-general-mtp-test-cases.html#sec:test-metrics-127" title="Permalink to this header"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></h3>

<ol>
<li>The EUT processes the certificate and establishes a secure TLS connection at the MTP layer.</li>
</ol>

